  "instructions": [
    "Heat the score fat in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the curry powder, turmeric, and salt, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in the english mustard and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the red lentils, water, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, until the lentils are tender, about 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped cilantro and season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve the curry hot over rice or with naan bread."
